---
# Suppress checks that are inappropriate for test code.
# Tests legitimately use magic numbers (test data values), dereference
# optionals after ASSERT_TRUE guards that tidy cannot follow, and use
# the idiomatic anonymous-namespace pattern rather than static.
Checks: >-
    -bugprone-unchecked-optional-access,
    -cppcoreguidelines-avoid-magic-numbers,
    -llvm-prefer-static-over-anonymous-namespace,
    -readability-magic-numbers
...
